version_description:
1. Magic crystals possess incredible summoning powers, check out what you can summon!
2. Mysterious evolving fish has special powers, try and tap them!
3. Miss Nana came from the mysterious sea, she brought the magic crystals and can direct fish where to go, check it out at the secret gate!
4. The musicians have learned a new song! Can't wait to hear it!
5. You can filter by labels in your backpack, filter any way you want!
